description:
This is a 362 minute workout called 'Cozy Kpop' from the channel Alexander Gogol.
The workout falls under Cardio/Walking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Mindful Walk and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The The Mindful Walk vibe means Meditative, story-driven, immersive. This is especially good for When you need fresh air, a change of pace, and mental clarity. The The Deep Recharge vibe means Nervous system reset, ultra-gentle movement. This is especially good for Times of extreme stress, fatigue, or mental overload..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
